FBIS4-63264 "drsov098_f_94030" FBIS-SOV-94-098 Daily Report 19 May 1994 National Affairs Government Approves Regulations on State Border Government Approves Regulations on State Border LD2005093994 Kiev UNIAR in Ukrainian 2155 GMT 19 May 94 LD2005093994 Kiev UNIAR Ukrainian BFN [Text] Kiev, 19 May -- The Ukrainian Cabinet of Ministers has approved a resolution on the creation of a border strip. It is being established along Ukraine's state border in areas of land, along the shores of frontier rivers, and within settlements and rural councils of people's deputies adjacent to the border. The border regime regulations were also confirmed.
